Extraordinary personal stories from around the world. Today, the American father who joined worried parents after a school shooting - then discovered his own son was the killer. The wildlife film-maker who spent four months living with half a million penguins, and the Philippine man who loves Superman so much, that he's had several operations to make himself look like the comic hero. Show less